    {
      "text": "The aircraft has three main variants: the conventional takeoff and landing F-35A, the short take-off and vertical-landing F-35B, and the catapult-assisted take-off but arrested recovery F-35C.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lockheed_Martin_F-35_Lightning_II",
